pjv.evolution

Class PJVEvolutionController

  • java.lang.Object
    • pjv.evolution.PJVEvolutionController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable, GuiCommunication

    public class PJVEvolutionController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable, GuiCommunication
    The main and only controller representing GUI for the genetic algorithm. This controller is connected to FXMLDocument.fxml in this package.
